  "1681840": {
    "name": "Abalon: Roguelike Tactics CCG",
    "steam_appid": 1681840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/0998da16c78022e9d178b6ee1653c482.avif?t=1767634553\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras_big/0998da16c78022e9d178b6ee1653c482.avif?t=1767634553 width=800 height=458 /></span><br><br>《召唤命途》是一款融合了传统回合制战斗和战略卡牌战斗的Roguelike冒险游戏。游戏的背景设定是一片叫做多元宇宙的幻想之地，你的任务是引导召唤师完成危险的任务，寻找隐藏的秘密、强大的卡牌和变异的兔子。<br><br>多元宇宙的灵感来自传统桌游设定，从冰霜的山峰到荒芜的沙漠，从多彩的林地到昏暗的地牢，每个世界都有独具特色的角色、谜题以及Boss。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/5870a0cf3d9f72aa85817c5067b00c1f.poster.avif?t=1767634553\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/5870a0cf3d9f72aa85817c5067b00c1f.webm?t=1767634553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/5870a0cf3d9f72aa85817c5067b00c1f.mp4?t=1767634553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/b72b9eb86b671366be82d0f2b460acc9.avif?t=1767634553\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>《召唤命途》从《Hero Quest》、《Talisman》等经典桌游汲取灵感，将战略性战斗与经过D20骰子决定的事件相结合。你可以实时探索多元宇宙，发现传说卷轴、购买强大卡牌，甚至可以参加哥布林的生日派对（别忘了上交黄金）。<br><br>战斗时，游戏就进入了回合制。每个单位所站的方位和你的法术同样重要。这些紧张刺激的遭遇战在竞技场风格的地图中展开，环境并不只是用来装饰的场景，而是战斗的关键一环。你可以在战斗中装备从雕像获取的盔甲，也可以把敌人推到尖刺墙上，甚至可以把敌方身后的一棵树变成你的盟友一起作战。你可以灵活运用战场来获得优势。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/9e78aa9da011bda103b1006f229378a3.poster.avif?t=1767634553\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/9e78aa9da011bda103b1006f229378a3.webm?t=1767634553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/9e78aa9da011bda103b1006f229378a3.mp4?t=1767634553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/8ed1073d1a82c068cc0fcbc902945f6a.avif?t=1767634553\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>在DnD风格的事件和杀敌的过程中，你能收集大量的卡牌。每个召唤师都有两种类型，包括奥术、天界、自然、虚空和混沌。每种类型都代表了不同的风格，比如混沌包含大量的火焰AOE法术，能造成巨大伤害；而奥术则有精神控制敌人的能力。<br><br>你的牌组上限是20张，你可以收集所有喜欢的卡牌，不用担心会妨碍牌组构筑。如果你想在冒险中途改变玩法，那么就在营火上烤些棉花糖，然后找灵龟聊聊天就行。<br><br>《召唤命途》的冒险不断变化，因此随机应变很重要。在对战模式中，你可以用在冒险中发现的卡牌构筑牌组。牌组完成后，再带上两个盟友，你可以测试自己的力量，对抗最为强悍的敌人！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/13326300600c96162b689b7256b0f740.poster.avif?t=1767634553\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/13326300600c96162b689b7256b0f740.webm?t=1767634553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/13326300600c96162b689b7256b0f740.mp4?t=1767634553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681840/extras/55a9665c3b40720113751a7695c710ab.avif?t=1767634553\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5个可供探索的世界，各自包含特色事件、角色以及Boss<br></li><li>20个召唤师可供选择，引导你完成冒险，每个召唤师都有独特的能力<br></li><li>50多个角色等你发现，每一个都可以加入你的冒险<br></li><li>400多张卡牌，你可以精心构筑专属于自己的完美牌组<br></li><li>PvE对战模式为你熟悉每个召唤师提供完美的竞技场</li></ul>",
